title: 1055 How To Overcome Negative Emotions, Let Go of Your Identity & Truly Love Yourself w/Dr. Joe Dispenza (PART 2)
description:
“The preparation for the day is to remind yourself who you no longer want to be.”

Today's guest is Dr. Joe Dispenza. Dr Joe’s interest lies in demystifying the mystical so that people have all the tools within their reach to make measurable changes in their lives. In today’s episode, Lewis and Dr. Joe dive deep into overcoming negative emotions, letting go of your identity, how to love yourself and so much more!

For more go to: www.lewishowes.com/1055

Greatness Coaching: www.lewishowes.com/coaching

Check out Dr. Joe's website: https://drjoedispenza.com/

Dr. Joe Dispenza on Healing the Body and Tranforming the Mind: https://link.chtbl.com/826-pod
